# Supabase Edge Functions

- Stack: Deno + Hono (not Prisma/Next). One function per folder under `src/supabase/functions/<domain>/`.
- `index.tsx`: HTTP routing only. Business logic in `services/`, repos in `internal/repositories/`.
- Dependency injection required (Supabase client, logger, config). No hardcoded secrets.
- Validate inputs with Zod. Standard responses: `{ success: true, data }` / `{ success: false, error: { code, message } }`.
- Use injected logger, not `console.*` in services. Deploy via `bash scripts/supabase-checked.sh functions deploy <name>`.
- Local dev: `npm run dev` (Docker Supabase) or `supabase functions serve` with `--workdir src`.
